      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The chassis maintains excellent turn-in response thanks to a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup, with the critical rear subframe mounting points recently inspected and reinforced. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved enthusiast vehicle, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering a linear power band up to the 8,000 RPM redline and exceptional thermal efficiency under load.",
